Summary stats

This mplads data is for the 14th and 15the Loksabha which commenced on 20004 and 2009 respectively. We matched it with Uttar Pradesh MPs for the same years.

Observations: 1, 42

Years : 2009 and 2014 - 25 and 31 dynast MPs respectively.

Main variables : Type of project and the cost incurred. Main categories of type of projects are Road, Electricity, Education, Construction, Water, Others, Sanitation

Two type of comparisons

Family v/s Non-family

This table shows the average number of projects and the cost for the family types. First table is for both years and the second one is year by year break-up of the same.

cost categories

We categorised the projects into three depending upon the cost of the project:

Categories:

Low - 0-.2 mn

Medium - 2.2 mn - 5 mn

High - 5 mn+
